window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An ideal starting point for those interested in Buddhism, <i>Being Peace</i> contains Thich Nhat Hanh's teachings on peace and meditation. </p> <p>Using real examples from his own life as well as poems and fables, Nhat Hanh explains his key practices for living \"right in the moment we are alive\". These lessons are taught with fine writing and sparkling phrases that draw the listener in and make <i>Being Peace</i> an audiobook that encourages multiple listenings. </p> <p>Still as timely as when it was first published over 25 years ago, <i>Being Peace</i> is a revelation for anyone concerned with the state of the world and the quality of life. </p>"; 
